  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/4d4cb0a16d51e296fbf79f7de7e1cd03.avif?t=1735337197\" width=600 height=92 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/da2aafffebd944abed87992cf9012af0.poster.avif?t=1735337197\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/da2aafffebd944abed87992cf9012af0.webm?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/da2aafffebd944abed87992cf9012af0.mp4?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Embark on an epic journey filled with action and mystery in 'The Unknown'. Follow Uriel, a small girl armed with an imposing sword, as she braves an unknown world in search of her  destiny. Get ready to dive into a 2D pixel art universe, full of challenges and secrets to be discovered.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/32f11909ccb689f12a296f69b0f4389d.avif?t=1735337197\" width=600 height=92 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELP URIEL FOLLOW HIS DESTINY</h2>]<br><strong>An enhancement system featuring randomized items that grant you the necessary power to progress through your journey.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/970c455c5b2e62ee7ad8455729bc7b39.poster.avif?t=1735337197\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/970c455c5b2e62ee7ad8455729bc7b39.webm?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/970c455c5b2e62ee7ad8455729bc7b39.mp4?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Level up system and status update mechanism.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/ef0a070f20e3602f00fd84a7c6a210e9.poster.avif?t=1735337197\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/ef0a070f20e3602f00fd84a7c6a210e9.webm?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/ef0a070f20e3602f00fd84a7c6a210e9.mp4?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>With an exciting mix of platforming and combat<br>Your swordsmanship will be put to the test as you face fearsome enemies in intense battles.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/6bca306f39a239bf338fe47d74f40326.poster.avif?t=1735337197\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/6bca306f39a239bf338fe47d74f40326.webm?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2422850/extras/6bca306f39a239bf338fe47d74f40326.mp4?t=1735337197\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Get ready to enter a world full of dangers and challenges, discover the secrets that await you in 'The Unknown'. Venture into this extraordinary journey and discover Uriel's destiny!.</strong>",
